metadata.name: Pumpkin Beetle
metadata.description:
The tiny beetle found in my garden.

Scientific name : Aulacophora femoralis

Aulacophora is a genus of beetles in the family Chrysomelidae, commonly known as 'Pumpkin beetle'.

This macro photograph was captured on Nikon D3300, with Reversing lens technique, handheld, manually focused. This is a single image and no manipulation or stacking is used to create this.
The beetle is alive.

Artist : Abhinand Reghu
Edition : 1/1
